'''草莓蛋糕'''（{{lang-en|Strawberry cake}}）是一种以草莓为主要原料的蛋糕<ref name="Mesnier Chattman 2007">{{cite book | last=Mesnier | first=R. | last2=Chattman | first2=L. | title=Roland Mesnier's Basic to Beautiful Cakes | publisher=Simon & Schuster | year=2007 | isbn=978-1-4165-4619-1 | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=jZgLvhLaioUC&pg=PA63 |  pages=63–72}}</ref>。

== 概述 ==
草莓蛋糕中可以使用麵糊，並在表面放上草莓；在[[千層蛋糕|千層蛋糕]]之間也可填充草莓，並任意组成<ref name="Wed 2015">{{cite web | author=Lambert, Alison | title=In season: Strawberry cake | website=Otago Daily Times | date=2015-12-02 | url=http://www.odt.co.nz/lifestyle/food-wine/recipes/365411/strawberry-cake | accessdate=2015-12-02 | archive-date=2015-12-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151204063339/http://www.odt.co.nz/lifestyle/food-wine/recipes/365411/strawberry-cake | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Byrn 2011">{{cite book | last=Byrn | first=A. | title=The Cake Mix Doctor’s 25 Best Birthday Cakes | publisher=Workman Publishing Company | series=Workman Shorts | year=2011 | isbn=978-0-7611-6348-0 | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=mqjZMQJAXLsC&pg=PA31 | pages=31–33}}</ref>；有些則是準備將草莓與糖霜結合<ref name="Lee 2005">{{cite book | last=Lee | first=S. | title=Sandra Lee Semi-Homemade Desserts | publisher=Wiley | series=Sandra Lee semi-homemade | year=2005 | isbn=978-0-696-22684-7 | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=MZZyo57ofXQC&pg=PA167 | page=167}}</ref><ref name="Miller 2015">{{cite book | last=Miller | first=W. | title=Whitney Miller's New Southern Table: My Favorite Family Recipes with a Modern Twist | publisher=Thomas Nelson | year=2015 | isbn=978-0-7180-1161-1 | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4smxCAAAQBAJ&pg=PA241 | pages=241–242}}</ref>。可以使用新鮮或冷凍的草莓<ref name="Mesnier Chattman 2007"/><ref name="Edmunds 2015 p. 8">{{cite book | last=Edmunds | first=K. | title=Destination Desserts | publisher=WestBow Press | year=2015 | isbn=978-1-4908-8254-3 | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=yuD8CQAAQBAJ&pg=PT8  | at=pts 8–11}}</ref>；有些則可能以草莓味明膠為原料，當和麵糊混合時，可以給蛋糕粉紅色的顏色<ref name="Mesnier Chattman 2007"/><ref name="Miller 2015"/><ref name="Edmunds 2015 p. 8"/><ref name="Graslie 2013">{{cite web | last=Graslie | first=Serri | title=Saving Grandma's Strawberry Cake From The Clutches Of Jell-O | website=NPR | date=2013-06-13 | url=http://www.npr.org/sections/thesalt/2013/06/13/190779038/Jell-O-No-Cutting-Out-Grandmas-Shortcuts-In-Strawberry-Cake | accessdate=2015-12-02 | archive-date=2015-11-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151128152924/http://www.npr.org/sections/thesalt/2013/06/13/190779038/Jell-O-No-Cutting-Out-Grandmas-Shortcuts-In-Strawberry-Cake | dead-url=no }}</ref>；一些草莓蛋糕裡面{{link-en|裝飾 (餐飲)|Garnish (food)|裝飾}}草莓，也可當作[[无麸质饮食|无麸质饮食]]小菜<ref name="Mesnier Chattman 2007"/><ref name="Byrn Fink 2010">{{cite book | last=Byrn | first=A. | last2=Fink | first2=B. | title=The Cake Mix Doctor Bakes Gluten-Free | publisher=Workman Publishing Company | year=2010 | isbn=978-0-7611-6098-4 | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Bgc1OJOLKBsC&pg=PA22 | pages=22–24}}</ref>。

一些說法是冷凍後並以部分凍結的狀態食用，[[里考塔|里考塔]]有時作為麵糊中的成分或者表面裝飾使用<ref name="Byrn 2011"/><ref name="yahoo.com 2015">{{cite web | title=5-Ingredient Strawberry Icebox Cake | website=Yahoo Food | date=2015-08-07 | url=https://www.yahoo.com/food/5-ingredient-strawberry-icebox-cake-this-time-of-126093788536.html | accessdate=2015-12-02 | archive-date=2015-12-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208062044/https://www.yahoo.com/food/5-ingredient-strawberry-icebox-cake-this-time-of-126093788536.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="McCormack 1989">{{cite book | last=McCormack | first=N.J. | title=Creative Quantity Cooking | publisher=Aspen Publishers | year=1989 | isbn=978-0-8342-0058-6 | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8oMD4_l5DFgC&pg=PA87 | pages=87–88}}</ref><ref name="Monitor 2015">{{cite web | title=Strawberry ricotta cake | website=The Christian Science Monitor | date=2015-06-08 | url=http://www.csmonitor.com/The-Culture/Food/Stir-It-Up/2015/0608/Strawberry-ricotta-cake | accessdate=2015-12-02 | archive-date=2015-12-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208164332/http://www.csmonitor.com/The-Culture/Food/Stir-It-Up/2015/0608/Strawberry-ricotta-cake | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="yahoo.com 2015-1">{{cite web | title=Cake of the Day: Ricotta Strawberry Cake | author=Yen, Donna | website=Yahoo Food | date=May 12, 2015 | url=https://www.yahoo.com/food/cake-of-the-day-ricotta-strawberry-cake-118800113661.html | accessdate=2015-12-02 | archive-date=2015-12-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208061221/https://www.yahoo.com/food/cake-of-the-day-ricotta-strawberry-cake-118800113661.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。草莓蛋糕有時以{{link-en|糕點裝飾|Cake decorating}}作為準備基礎，如白色蛋糕組合附加成分添加到麵糊或者蛋糕表面上<ref name="Detroit News 2015">{{cite web | title='Best ever' strawberry cake starts with a mix | website=Detroit News | date=2015-01-13 | url=http://www.detroitnews.com/story/life/food/2015/01/13/best-ever-strawberry-cake-starts-mix/21404189/ | accessdate=2015-12-02 | archive-date=2015-12-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208122810/http://www.detroitnews.com/story/life/food/2015/01/13/best-ever-strawberry-cake-starts-mix/21404189/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>；有時會在情人節準備並作為菜餚<ref name="Pierce 2015">{{cite web | last=Pierce | first=Kim | title=10 Valentine's Day gift ideas for people who don’t like chocolate | website=Dallas Morning News | date=2015-02-03 | url=http://www.dallasnews.com/lifestyles/food-wine/food-wine-headlines/20150203-10-valentine-s-day-gift-ideas-for-people-who-dont-like-chocolate.ece | accessdate=2015-12-02 | archive-date=2015-12-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208155020/http://www.dallasnews.com/lifestyles/food-wine/food-wine-headlines/20150203-10-valentine-s-day-gift-ideas-for-people-who-dont-like-chocolate.ece | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 菲律賓 ==
===本格特省拉特立尼達的草莓節===
2004年3月20日，世界上最大的草莓蛋糕在世界紀錄確認是由幾名麵包師製作共重{{convert|21,213.40|lb|kg}}的蛋糕，並由吉尼斯編制<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/largest-fruit-shortcake/ | title=Largest fruit shortcake | publisher=Guinness World Records | accessdate=2015-12-02 | archive-date=2016-08-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811210026/http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/largest-fruit-shortcake | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年3月，6,000片用新鮮草莓製成切片草莓蛋糕作為活動組成的一部分，並提供的其他食物包括草莓[[椰絲糯米糕|椰絲糯米糕]]和[[果酒|草莓酒]]<ref name="GMA News Online 2015">{{cite web | title=Get ready for 6,000 slices of strawberry cake in Benguet | author=Locsin, Joel | website=GMA News and Public Affairs | date=2015-08-10 | url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/452393/lifestyle/food/get-ready-for-6-000-slices-of-strawberry-cake-in-benguet | accessdate=2015-12-02 | archive-date=2015-12-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208115739/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/452393/lifestyle/food/get-ready-for-6-000-slices-of-strawberry-cake-in-benguet | dead-url=no }}</ref>；一些麵包店和餐館將草莓蛋糕作為加收票價的一部分<ref>{{cite web | title=Strawberry cake forever | website=Los Angeles Times | date=2009-09-30 | url=http://www.latimes.com/food/la-fo-phoenixcake30-2009sep30-story.html | accessdate=2015-12-02 | archive-date=2015-12-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208052502/http://www.latimes.com/food/la-fo-phoenixcake30-2009sep30-story.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

這個蛋糕已經成為[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]{{link-en|拉特立尼達 (本格特省)|La Trinidad, Benguet|拉特立尼達}}{{link-en|草莓節|Strawberry festival}}的一部份。

